Package: geotax
Type: Package
Title: Tools for exploring taxonomical distance over the geographical space
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Angel Luis Robles Fernandez
Maintainer: Angel Luis Robles Fernandez <a.l.robles.fernandez@gmail.com>
Description: This is a set of tools to model the probability that two potential
    host (or other clases of interactions) share a pathogen given a phylogenetyc 
    or taxonomical distance.
